  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If I do nothing else, at least this I must do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I agreed to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was after a crisis in our family, because I was discovered that it was on a Rosh Hashanah, not Yom Kippur, under the prayers book, I was reading another book.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was the result of my studying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had my doubts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You see, I always, as a child placed myself into another position.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I told that if I were God, I wouldn't be very much impressed by people telling me how great I am and grant them favor just because they say so.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I found the long services a bit boring and I covered the book towards my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But a neighbor on the other side, I was very upset at him because he reported me to my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At which point, he went to the chief rabbi to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He always went to him even before important business decisions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I heard what he said, and it was very interesting how [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] strong and considerate our religion is, because he told him that he need not to be concerned, because he did what was his part, that he showed me the right way.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the rest is in between God and me, and he should rest assured that, when the time comes, I will find the right way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So at which point, he accepted that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was extremely concerned, not so much about how God will accept or reject my transgression, but about Him.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
